This paper is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category as it deals with video streaming and quality-of-experience metrics. It may also fall under the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) category as it discusses the wireless channel model and bandwidth efficiency. Additionally, it could be categorized under Graphics (cs.GR) as it deals with virtual reality and 360-degree scenes. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is also a possibility as it involves predicting the field-of-view of each user. Finally, Information Theory (cs.IT) may be relevant as the paper mentions using convex optimization to find a feasible solution.
